title: Couple With Heart Woman Person Light Skin Tone No Skin Tone
description: Illustrates a romantic couple consisting of a person and a man, with a heart indicating their affection and connection. It's used to express love and partnership.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this couple emoji features a woman with a light skin tone and a person with no specified skin tone, their forms depicted with Apple's signature smooth, rounded edges and gentle 3D shading. A bright, glossy heart, rendered with realistic highlights, floats between them, signifying their deep affection and bond. This heartwarming representation of love and connection on Apple devices is perfect for celebrating relationships and shared emotions.
